6.query: SELECT ?p ?pname ?s ?sname ?composer_name ?citizenship WHERE { ?s ?p wd:Q172980; wdt:P86 ?cname. ?cname wdt:P27 ?coun. ?s sc:name ?sname . ?p sc:name ?pname . ?cname sc:name ?composer_name. ?coun sc:name ?citizenship. } LIMIT 10
